    <note>Liu(2) Fa(2) [22909] See documentation in 1148 jinshi list, erjia #3, for son, Jipei [22911]. Fa(2) earned the juren degree in 1105, probably in Kaifeng, and then moved south. He was deceased when Jipei earned the degree in 1148. Jipei's elder brother, Yong(4) [22910], is identified in the 1148 list as the founder of the family (weihu). Sanshan zhi, 28.8b.</note>
